# VectorForge Environment Variables

# =============================================================================
# OpenAI Configuration (Default)
# =============================================================================
# Get your API key from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-openai-api-key-here

# =============================================================================
# Alternative: Azure AI Foundry Configuration
# =============================================================================
# If using Azure OpenAI instead, uncomment and fill these in:
# Get these values from your Azure Portal under Azure OpenAI resource

# AZURE_OPENAI_ENDPOINT=https://your-resource-name.openai.azure.com/
# AZURE_OPENAI_API_KEY=your-azure-openai-api-key-here
# AZURE_OPENAI_DEPLOYMENT_NAME=gpt-4o

# =============================================================================
# Notes
# =============================================================================
# 1. Copy this file to .env (which is gitignored)
# 2. Fill in your actual API keys
# 3. Never commit .env to version control
# 4. Restart your dev server after making changes
# 5. For production/GitHub deployment, set these as GitHub Secrets
#
# See ENVIRONMENT_SETUP.md for detailed setup instructions
